from scipy.stats import chi2_contingency

# contingency table for Complaint Type vs Resolution Time
complaint_time_table = pd.crosstab(index=df['Complaint Type'], columns=df['Request_Closing_Time'])

# perform chi-square test
chi2, p, dof, expected = chi2_contingency(complaint_time_table)

# print p-value and odds ratio
print('Complaint Type:')
print('p-value =', p)
print('odds ratio =', expected[0, 0] / expected[1, 0])
